298
00:14:34,331 --> 00:14:39,753
Fights between various
segments of the city and Blacks.

299
00:14:39,837 --> 00:14:41,881
[police radio chatter]

300
00:14:41,964 --> 00:14:46,135
When I graduated
junior high school in '68,

301
