331
00:16:00,501 --> 00:16:05,631
And he was a Democrat,
but he could play to that side.

332
00:16:05,714 --> 00:16:07,424
And that created tension.

333
00:16:07,508 --> 00:16:09,510
[chanting]

334
00:16:09,593 --> 00:16:14,473
[Sharpton]: That led all the
way up to Bernhard Goetz, '84.

335
00:16:14,556 --> 00:16:17,267
'85 was the mayor's race.

336
00:16:17,476 --> 00:16:19,144
And '86 was Howard Beach.

337
00:16:19,228 --> 00:16:23,857
