They never welcomed Black
people in this neighborhood.

342
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,327
See a Black person,
a colored person,

343
00:16:35,411 --> 00:16:37,997
first thing is you yell
at them, you know?

344
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,957
This is the way it is
in this neighborhood.

345
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:41,709
We had great
leaders in New York--

346
00:16:41,792 --> 00:16:43,877
Adam Powell, Malcolm X, and all.

347
00:16:43,961 --> 00:16:47,965
