side with you or through you.

350
00:16:56,765 --> 00:17:00,144
{\an8}It's gotta be with
dignity and integrity!

351
00:17:00,227 --> 00:17:02,312
We don't want any
more than you have,

352
00:17:02,396 --> 00:17:05,107
