358
00:17:20,873 --> 00:17:24,626
[shouts of "Nigger!"]

359
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,461
Racism, huh?

360
00:17:25,544 --> 00:17:26,670
Tell the fucker go home.

361
00:17:26,753 --> 00:17:28,881
