00:17:57,701 --> 00:17:59,953
[Sharpton]: All
of the activists,

375
00:18:00,037 --> 00:18:03,123
the ones that I've
studied and emulated,

376
00:18:03,207 --> 00:18:07,586
came at a time when
what we wanted to say,

