1564
01:17:18,592 --> 01:17:22,220
[applause]

1565
01:17:23,430 --> 01:17:26,224
[Sharpton]: George Floyd's story

1566
01:17:26,308 --> 01:17:28,894
has been the
story of Black folks,

1567
01:17:28,977 --> 01:17:34,274
because ever
