we're trying to be.

2196
01:49:05,580 --> 01:49:06,748
It's crazy.

2197
01:49:06,831 --> 01:49:08,458
{\an8}[Alcindor]: Nobody was
tested. It was just crazy.

2198
01:49:08,542 --> 01:49:10,794
{\an8}We tested everybody, and
those that we had to let in

2199
01:49:10,877 --> 01:49:12,963
{\an8}we tested in
brackets in the back.

2200
01:49:13,046 --> 01:49:13,713
{\an8}Yeah.

2201
