[Man]: Show me what
democracy looks like!

2210
01:49:35,735 --> 01:49:38,405
[Group]: This is what
democracy looks like!

2211
01:49:38,530 --> 01:49:42,409
[Sharpton]: You slowly helped
some families to understand

2212
