We can't bring 'em
back. I wish we could.

2217
01:49:54,754 --> 01:49:56,047
[Reporter]: Reverend Sharpton,

2218
01:49:56,131 --> 01:49:57,632
What is your call to action?

2219
01:49:57,716 --> 01:50:03,430
We want to push the George
Floyd Policing and Justice bill

2220
01:50:03,513 --> 01:50:04,848
