2221
01:50:04,931 --> 01:50:07,684
They ought to go to
their senators, email them,

2222
01:50:07,767 --> 01:50:09,394
and say those bills must pass.

2223
01:50:09,477 --> 01:50:12,439
But we can make
a historic statement

2224
01:50:12,522 --> 01:50:13,773
if we just work together.

2225
01:50:13,857 --> 01:50:17,360
{\an8}Anything you need, let us
know. All right? Anything.

2226
01:50:17,444 --> 01:50:20,697
{\an8}I'm gonna give you my
number if you need anything.

2227
01:50:25,619 --> 01:50:29,456
{\an8}You have to have somebody
that's been there with them,

2228
01:50:29,539 --> 01:50:31,333
{\an8}they know what to talk about,

2229
01:50:31,416 --> 01:50:32,959
{\an8}that's not coming in
with platitudes and all,

2230
01:50:33,043 --> 01:50:36,379
but they're coming
with real-life stuff.

2231
01:50:36,463 --> 01:50:37,380
And I've been there.

2232
01:50:37,464 --> 01:50:39,466
[cheers and applause]

2233
01:50:39,549 --> 01:50:44,679
[Sharpton]: When I go up,
have Mr. Blake, Philonise Floyd,

2234
01:50:44,763 --> 01:50:48,141
Breonna's mother, and
Arbery's father standing,

2235
01:50:48,224 --> 01:50:50,310
