We're dealing with a police
case in Columbus, Ohio.

2407
01:59:30,246 --> 01:59:32,540
Dealing with a shooting
in North Carolina.

2408
01:59:32,623 --> 01:59:35,293
We're dealing with
the killing here, Daunte.

2409
01:59:35,376 --> 01:59:37,003
If now is not the time,

2410
01:59:37,086 --> 01:59:39,964
I don't know when it
ever will be the time.

2411
01:59:40,047 --> 01:59:42,133
[Reporter]: Reverend Al
Sharpton, thank you so much,

2412
01:59:42,216 --> 01:59:45,011
